0and%20tourism%2C%20placing%20a%20strain%20on%20the%20hotel%20sector%20that%20could%20also%20damage%20that%20segment's%20appeal%20to%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20buying%20a%20property%2C%20when%20I'm%20bidding%2C%20I%20want%20to%20underwrite%20every%20worst-case%20scenario%20and%20put%20that%20into%20my%20bid%20so%20that%20I%20protect%20myself%20from%20downsides%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Costello%2C%20the%20co-head%20of%20MSCI's%20real%20assets%20research%20team.%20%26quot%3BThe%20increase%20in%20uncertainty%20will%20increase%20the%20disconnect%20between%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20and%2C%20you%20increase%20the%20disconnect%20between%20buyers%20and%20sellers%2C%20you'll%20have%20lower%20deal%20volume.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227458ae26-8da2-43ac-98df-a27ffb6bfb1b%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSurvive%20until%202025%26quot%3B%20mantra%20fades%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20President%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-style-presidency-real-estate-developer-deal-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereceived%20favorably%20by%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20property%20industry.%20Trump's%20family%20business%20is%20in%20real%20estate%20development%20and%20investment%2C%20and%20he%20is%20viewed%20as%20sensitive%20to%20the%20sector's%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimism%20about%20a%20rebound%20was%20so%20great%20that%20it%20spawned%20a%20popular%20saying%20in%20the%20industry%3A%20Survive%20until%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20tariffs%20on%20imports%2C%20including%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-trump-steel-aluminum-tiles-development-real-estate-construction-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20materials%20like%20steel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20driven%20up%20prices%20for%20goods%2C%20raising%20renewed%20concerns%20about%20inflation%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20leeway%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRates%20aren't%20coming%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Barry%20Sternlicht%2C%20the%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Starwood%20Capital%20Group%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%2C%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20rates%20would%20be%20coming%20down%20and%20I%20thought%20that%20would%20unleash%20a%20lot%20of%20trades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternlicht%20said%20that%20Starwood%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20investment%20firm%20that%20manages%20about%20%24115%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20has%20held%20off%20putting%20properties%20on%20the%20market%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20put%20it%20out%20if%20we%20don't%20think%20we%20can%20sell%20it%20at%20the%20right%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Sternlicht%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20haven't%20put%20stuff%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20quarter%20earnings%20statement%2C%20Starwood%20reported%20%26quot%3Bno%20significant%20acquisitions%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20sales%20of%20property.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20the%20company%20reported%20that%20it%20had%20sold%2016%20retail%20properties%20for%20%24387.1%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20%2426.1%20billion%20of%20commercial%20property%20was%20sold%20in%20April%20nationally%2C%20according%20to%20MSCI%2C%20equal%20to%20the%20same%20month%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20sales%20market%20had%20been%20on%20a%20rebound%2C%20with%20%24449.1%20billion%20of%20transactions%20in%20the%20prior%2012-month%20period%2C%20a%2017%25%20increase%20year%20over%20year%2C%20according%20to%20MSCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20not%20every%20market%20in%20the%20country%20has%20been%20hit%20as%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Blackstone%20reached%20a%20deal%20to%20purchase%20an%20ownership%20interest%201345%20Avenue%20of%20the%20Americas%2C%20a%20large%20Manhattan%20office%20tower.%20RXR%2C%20another%20New%2