d.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Stephen%20Goudeau%2C%20I'm%20the%20head%20of%20the%20brand.%20When%20I%20go%20to%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20I%20can%20relax%20a%20little%20because%20somebody%20else%20is%20in%20charge.%20I%20can%20concentrate%20on%20my%20day-to-day%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20knows%20that%20I%20have%20my%20own%20fashion%20company.%20Having%20a%20brand%20hasn't%20stopped%20me%20from%20progressing%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd8b7d04-6ea4-449d-ae46-50891241a949%5C%22%3EWhen%20I%20get%20home%20from%20my%20day%20job%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20my%20designs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20I'm%20tired%2C%20it's%20not%20hard%20to%20get%20inspired.%20My%20apartment%20is%20full%20of%20mannequins.%20I%20may%20work%20until%201%20a.m.%2C%20but%20I%20only%20need%20three%20or%20four%20hours%20of%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evenings%2C%20I%20have%20calls%20with%20my%20fashion%20company%20and%20a%20team%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20nights.%20Having%20a%20solid%20team%20behind%20me%20ensures%20I%20don't%20get%20swamped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8decef4-d8b4-4769-8eee-49a61d0efa26%5C%22%3EThe%20upsides%20of%20having%20two%20jobs%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20finances%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20AT%26amp%3BT%20has%20also%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20running%20a%20business.%20I%20get%20to%20work%20with%20a%20larger%20team%20and%20see%20different%20personalities%20and%20how%20different%20people%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20sacrificing%20the%20time%20I%20get%20to%20spend%20with%20my%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20guilty%20sometimes%2C%20but%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20my%20biggest%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stay%20on%20track%20through%20positive%20thoughts.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20every%20day%2C%20I%20put%20my%20feet%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20tell%20myself%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20a%20good%20day%20because%20we%20have%20the%20power%20to%20predict%20how%20our%20day%20will%