iguring%20he%20could%20generate%20quality%20returns%20by%20listing%20it%20on%20Airbnb.%20And%20that's%20essentially%20what%20happened%3A%20Reyna%20and%20the%20seller%2C%20who%20had%20built%20the%20tiny%20home%20on%20his%20own%20land%2C%20agreed%20on%20seller%20financing%20for%20the%20%2450%2C000%20property.%20Plus%2C%20the%20seller%20agreed%20to%20lease%20his%20land%20to%20Reyna%2C%20saving%20him%20the%20headache%20of%20finding%2C%20buying%2C%20and%20preparing%20another%20plot%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20renting%20it%20out%20on%20Airbnb%20immediately%2C%20and%20it%20took%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20foot%20traffic%20on%20the%20property%20increased%2C%20the%20landowner%20wanted%20more%20privacy%20and%20gave%20Reyna%20six%20months%20to%20move%20the%20tiny%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2206fa8f02-6628-4bf9-8da4-35845f37bc2c%5C%22%3EBuying%201.6%20acres%20of%20land%20for%20%2465%2C000%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EReyna's%20first%20obstacle%20was%20figuring%20out%20where%20to%20put%20the%20tiny%20home.%20He%20had%20two%20main%20criteria%20for%20the%20land%3A%20It%20had%20to%20be%20within%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20from%20his%20home%20and%20a%20place%20where%20people%20were%20already%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%2C%20stick%20tiny%20homes%20there%2C%20and%20then%20have%20to%20create%20some%20sort%20of%20buzz%20to%20get%20people%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22manny%20reyna%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839b3dcca50259add4d577f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReyna%20and%20his%20family%20moved%20from%20San%20Antonio%20to%20Tokyo%20in%202025.%3Cp%3EManny%20Reyna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20software%20tool%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airdna.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirDNA%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20helps%20investors%20find%20top%20short-term%20rental%20markets%20helped%20narrow%20his%20search%2C%20and%20he%20eventually%20settled%20on%20an%20area%20near%20Medina%20Lake.%20As%20for%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20land%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20things%20that%20I%20wanted%20were%20no%20HOA%20and%20no%20deed%20restrictions.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20spend%20a%20bunch%20of%20money%20getting%20permits%20and%20cutting%20through%20all%20this%20red%20tape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20who%20had%20connected%20him%20with%20the%20tiny%20home%20builder%2C%20helped%20him%20land%20a%20deal%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20that%20met%20his%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Texas%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20land%20was%20going%20for%20close%20to%20%2480%2C000%20an%20acre%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna%2C%20who%20found%20a%20motivated%20seller%20and%20paid%20%2465%2C000%20for%20his%201.6%20acres.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20lucky.%20The%20lady%20that%20I%20bought%20the%20land%20from%20had%20inherited%20it%2C%20and%20she%20didn't%20want%20it%20at%20all.%20She%20took%20the%20first%20offer%20that%20I%20gave%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20secured%20the%20land%20without%20much%20upfront%20cash%20by%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glo.texas.gov%2Fveterans%2Floans-veterans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20VLB%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20program%20that%20allows%20veterans%20in%20Texas%20to%20buy%20land%20with%20competitive%20interest%20rates%20and%20low%20down%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20bought%20land%20before.%20It's%20a%20whole%20other%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20took%20four%20months%20to%20close.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20buy%20the%20land%2C%20you%20need%20to%20get%20a%20surveyor%2C%20which%20is%20like%20an%20engineer%20who%20looks%20at%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20land%2C%20maps%20it%20all%20out%20for%20you%2C%20and%20gives%20you%20a%20certificate%20saying%2C%20this%20is%20what%20your%20land%20looks%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surveyor%20was%20the%20first%20of%20many%20professionals%20Reyna%20would%20hire%20to%20prepare%20the%20land%20for%20the%20tiny%20home%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bb5deaf-821f-4b77-95fc-eaf34e0620f4%5C%22%3ERacking%20up%20%2420%2C000%20in%20credit%20card%20debt%20to%20complete%20the%20project%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EReyna's%20next%20hires%20included%20a%20land-clearing%20company%20to%20prepare%20the%20land%20and%20a%20moving%20company%20to%20transport%20the%20tiny%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movers%20%26quot%3Bdropped%20it%20on%20some%20cement%20blocks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20on%20wheels%20or%20anything%20%E2%80%94%20it%20sits%20on%20cement%20blocks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20lie%2C%20it%20didn't%20look%20very%20nice%20aesthetically%20at%20first.%20So%2C%20I%20had%20to%20go%20build%20a%20deck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20added%20an%20eight-foot%20privacy%20fence%20around%20the%20home%20that%20cost%20about%20%244%2C800.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20land%20came%20with%20a%20water%20meter%2C%20which%20saved%20him%20from%20drilling%20a%20well%2C%20but%20that%20was%20about%20it.%20His%20largest%20expense%20was%20installing%20a%20septic%20system%2C%20a%20complex%20process%20that%20cost%20him%20about%20%2415%2C000%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20required%20a%20permit%20because%20it's%20considered%20a%20plumbing%20system%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20talk%20to%20specialists.%20They%20charged%20me%20to%20design%20it%20and%20install%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstalling%20electricity%20cost%20him%20another%20%243%2C400%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%241%2C900%20for%20the%20pole%20setup%2C%20plus%20another%20%241%2C500%20for%20trenching%20and%20wiring%20%E2%80%94%20and%20required%20independent%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20electrician%20asked%2C%20'What%20volts%20do%20you%20want%3F'%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20have%20no%20idea%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20that%20goes%20into%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22manny%20reyna%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839b0a4c6ad288d14823562%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReyna%20spent%20nearly%20%245%2C000%20building%20a%20privacy%20fence%20around%20his%20first%20tiny%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Manny%20Reyna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20funded%20the%20tiny%20home%20relocation%20and%20build-out%20project%20with%20rental%20income%20from%20his%20single-family%20home%20and%20savings%20from%20his%20full-time%20project%20management%20job.%20He%20also%20used%20two%20credit%20cards%20with%20%2420%2C000%20limits%20and%20long%200%25%20interest%20periods%3A%2015%20and%2021%20months.%20He%20split%20his%20expenses%20between%20the%20two%20cards%20to%20maximize%20the%20promo%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20racked%20up%20a%20roughly%20%2420%2C000%20balance%20between%20the%20two%20cards%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20questioned%20my%20life%20choices%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%20and%20wondered%2C%20'What%20am%20I%20doing%3F%20Is%20this%20going%20to%20be%20completely%20botched%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20admitted.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20that's%20part%20of%20it%2C%20right%3F%20Maybe%20if%20you%20don't%20question%20yourself%20or%20if%20you%20don't%20feel%20that%20way%2C%20maybe%20you're%20not%20doing%20things%20the%20right%20way%20or%20pushing%20the%20envelope%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20long%20and%20expensive%20months%20developing%20the%20land%2C%20he%20reopened%20his%20first%20tiny%20home%20for%20business%20in%20July%202023.%20He%20threw%20all%20of%20his%20profit%2C%20plus%20savings%20from%20his%20W-2%2C%20toward%20his%20credit%20card%20debt%20in%20order%20to%20pay%20it%20off%20before%20incurring%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20only%20costs%20I%20really%20have%20are%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20land%20and%20the%20utilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20carrying%20cost%20of%20the%20land%20is%20about%20%24400%2C%20and%20his%20monthly%20%26quot%3Bmortgage%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20%24290%20payment%20that%20goes%20directly%20to%20the%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1af257b-f4b6-4911-84dc-c34b71c8e9fb%5C%22%3EBringing%20in%20up%20to%20%241%2C500%20a%20month%20and%20adding%20a%20second%20tiny%20home%20to%20the%20land%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EReyna%20initially%20listed%20the%20tiny%20home%20as%20a%20short-term%20rental%20just%20on%20Airbnb%2C%20but%20now%20uses%20a%20variety%20of%20platforms%2C%20including%20VRBO%2C%20Hipcamp%2C%20Facebook%20Marketplace%2C%20and%20Furnished%20Finder%2C%20and%20offers%20it%20as%20a%20mid-term%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20do%20a%20shotgun%20approach%20to%20see%20who's%20going%20to%20bite%20first%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20solely%20relying%20on%20Airbnb%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20prefers%20mid-term%20stays%20(more%20than%2030%20days%20but%20less%20than%20a%20year).%20He's%20found%20this%20strategy%20to%20be%20more%20lucrative%20than%20renting%20to%20long-term%20tenants%20and%20much%20easier%20to%20manage%20than%20short-term%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22manny%20reyna%20casita%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f45c1c19ab3675c10902d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReyna%20set%20up%20a%20stock%20tank%20pool%20outside%20his%20first%20tiny%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Manny%20Reyna%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20first%20tiny%20home%20started%20profiting%20consistently%20%E2%80%94%20on%20average%2C%20he%20said%20it%20does%20between%20%241%2C200%20and%20%241%2C500%20a%20month%20in%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20Reyna%20added%20a%20second%20tiny%20home%20to%20his%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cool%20thing%20with%20the%20tiny%20homes%20is%20that%20they're%20so%20cheap%20to%20set%20up%20that%20the%20cash-on-cash%20return%20is%20pretty%20good%20once%20you%20can%20establish%20them%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna%2C%20who%20plans%20to%20add%20more%20properties%20to%20his%20lot.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20get%20more%20than%20one%20going%2C%20it's%20just%20pure%20profit%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20too%20much%20maintenance%2C%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20experimenting%20with%20other%20ways%20to%20%26quot%3Bhack%26quot%3B%20his%20land%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe've%20added%20two%20RV%20plug%20and%20play%20connections%20to%20the%20land%2C%20which%20we%20expect%20to%20bring%20in%20%24900%20to%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20and%20we've%20listed%20a%20plot%20of%20the%20land%20to%20rent%20through%20Sniffspot%2C%20which%20we%20estimate%20revenue%20to%20be%20%24200%20to%20%24300%20a%20month.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20his%20current%20rentals%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20on%20track%20to%20earn%20about%20%2485%2C000%20in%202025.%20BI%20verified%20his%20property%20ownership%20by%20looking%20at%20deeds%20and%20confirmed%20that%20he's%20bringing%20in%20rental%20income%20by%20viewing%20screenshots%20of%20his%20Airbnb%20dashboard%20and%20reviewing%20one%20of%20his%20mid-term%20rental%20lease%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tiny%20houses%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20making%20the%20most%20profit%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reyna%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20early%202025%20and%20moved%20to%20Tokyo%20with%20his%20family.%20He%20has%20a%20team%20in%20Texas%20that%20helps%20him%20manage%20the%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20classifies%20the%20tiny%20home%20project%20as%20a%20success%2C%20but%20if%20he%20could%20go%20back%20in%20time%2C%20he'd%20do%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20trying%20to%20build%20the%20plane%20before%20flying%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20His%20top%20advice%20for%20prospective%20tiny%20home%20investors%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Blook%20at%20everything%20from%20an%20all-encompassing%20view.%20Consider%20the%20cost%20of%20everything%20so%20that%20you're%20not%20figuring%20it%20out%20as%20you%20go%2C%20like%20I%20did.%20Also%2C%20try%20to%20find%20land%20with%20infrastructure%20already%20built%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20a%20water%20meter%2C%20because%20it's%20so%20expensive%20to%20get%20a%20well.%20If%20you%20can%20help%20it%2C%20electricity%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-it-costs-to-set-up-a-tiny-home-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749027602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f45e29b2a601d01b239b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-it-costs-to-set-up-a-tiny-home-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Real%20estate%20investor%20Manny%20Reyna%20shares%20all%20of%20the%20unexpected%20costs%20that%20came%20with%20setting%20up%20a%20tiny%20home%2C%20including%20how%20much%20he%20paid%20for%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-it-costs-to-set-up-a-tiny-home-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20a%20top%20Microsoft%20exec%20learned%20from%20Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%2C%20per%20an%20internal%20email%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jay%20Parikh%20(left)%20and%20Andy%20Jassy%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f73319d73a0031e8dcfc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigca