0These%20structures%20have%20become%20more%20common%20as%20overall%20deal%20flow%20remains%20subdued%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20spent%20decades%20watching%20the%20industry%20transform%20from%20a%20niche%20to%20a%20must-have%20strategy.%20Many%20of%20them%20didn't%20even%20know%20what%20secondary%20investing%20was%20when%20they%20were%20first%20recruited%20but%20are%20now%20leading%20this%20growing%20business%20at%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20powerful%20investment%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20Business%20Insider's%20first%20list%20of%20secondaries%20power%20players%2C%20highlighting%2015%20top%20professionals%20in%20this%20budding%20industry%2C%20presented%20in%20alphabetical%20order%20by%20firm%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJeffrey%20Akers%2C%20Adams%20Street%2C%20partner%20and%20head%20of%20secondary%20investments%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Akers%2C%20Adams%20Street%20standing%20in%20a%20suit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f0ff9c6ad288d1482621a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Akers%2C%20Partner%20%26amp%3B%20Head%20of%20Secondary%20Investments%2C%20Adams%20Street%3Cp%3EAdams%20Street%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAkers%20got%20his%20start%20as%20an%20investment%20banker%20at%20a%20regional%20bank%2C%20researching%20the%20private%20markets%20long%20before%20every%20private%20equity%20buyer%20was%20just%20a%20Google%20search%20away.%20His%20early%20experience%20evaluating%20private%20equity%20managers%20helped%20lead%20Akers%20to%20join%20Adams%20Street%20nearly%2020%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20secondaries%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20now%20led%20the%20firm's%20secondary%20investing%20team%20for%20nearly%20nine%20years%2C%20helping%20grow%20its%20assets%20under%20management%20to%20%248.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAkers%20said%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20%3C