nd%20Tristram%20Perkins%2C%20managing%20directors%20and%20global%20co-heads%20of%20NB%20Secondary%20Private%20Equity%2C%20Neuberger%20Berman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f19fcca50259add4d84fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222976%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBen%20Perl%20and%20Tristram%20Perkins%2C%20managing%20directors%20and%20global%20co-heads%20of%20NB%20Secondary%20Private%20Equity%2C%20Neuberger%20Berman%3Cp%3ENeuberger%20Berman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerkins%20has%20been%20investing%20in%20secondary%20private%20markets%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20beginning%20his%20career%20at%20the%20storied%20Wall%20Street%20firm%20Bankers%20Trust%20before%20its%20acquisition%20by%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%201999.%20A%20veteran%20of%20the%20space%2C%20Perkins%20is%20bullish%20on%20today's%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20invested%20in%20secondary%20private%20equity%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20this%20appears%20to%20me%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20attractive%20environments%20I%20have%20experienced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Deutsche%20Bank%20exited%20its%20private%20equity%20investments%2C%20Perkins%20and%20some%20of%20his%20Bankers%20Trust%20colleagues%20jumped%20to%20Neuberger%20Berman%2C%20launching%20the%20firm's%20secondaries%20platform%20with%20an%20%24800%20million%20fund%20in%202005.%20Neuberger's%20secondaries%20business%20has%20since%20raised%20%2420%20billion%20for%20secondaries%20investments%2C%20including%20a%20real%20estate%20secondaries%20arm%20helmed%20by%20Scott%20Koenig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerl%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20firm%20after%20working%20as%20a%20private%20equity%20investor%20for%20Lehman%20Brothers%2C%20eventually%20joined%20Perkins's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20loved%20about%20the%20secondary%20market%20was%20the%20opportunity%20to%20complete%20dozens%20of%20investments%20in%20a%20given%20year%2C%20Perl%20said.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20my%20peers%20at%20buyouts%20firms%20only%20make%20one%20or%20two%20investments%20a%20year%2C%20and%20some%20years%20they%20don't%20make%20any%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20a%20managing%20director%2C%20Perl%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20expanding%20Neuberger's%20secondaries%20platform%2C%20which%20has%20completed%20over%20%2416%20billion%20in%20GP-led%20deals%20across%2055%20transactions%20since%20its%20founding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerl%20said%20he'd%20seen%20deals%20grow%20more%20complicated%20as%20the%20industry%20matured%2C%20especially%20financial%20sponsor%20deals.%20He%20recalled%20a%20recent%20GP-led%20transaction%20involving%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%20managing%20five%20companies%20within%20a%20%245%20billion%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20they%20said%20to%20me%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20process%20was%20that%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20transactions%20they%20had%20ever%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Perl%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20it%20was%20like%20landing%20five%20planes%20simultaneously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-secondaries-power-players-blackstone-ares-goldman-sachs-clipway2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749027602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839e5a2ca50259add4d5eea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-secondaries-power-players-blackstone-ares-goldman-sachs-clipway2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Blackstone%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs%3A%20Meet%2014%20execs%20who%20helped%20lead%20private%20equity's%20secondaries%20market%20to%20a%20record%20%24160%20billion%20in%20deals%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engage