0the%20venture%20and%20startup%20mindset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir's%20practice%20of%20embedding%20engineers%20directly%20with%20clients%20to%20solve%20problems%20eventually%20evolved%20into%20a%20core%20company%20ethos%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BForward%20Deployed%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20essentially%20prioritizes%20speed%20and%20efficiency%2C%20taking%20definitive%20action%2C%20and%20working%20hand-in-hand%20with%20clients%20to%20see%20and%20solve%20problems%20up%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Forward%20Deployed%20Software%20Engineers%20are%20perhaps%20the%20most%20well%20known%2C%20Palantir%20has%20other%20forward-deployed%20teams%20throughout%20the%20organization%2C%20including%20a%20Forward%20Deployed%20Infrastructure%20Engineering%20team%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Baseline%20team%2C%20that%20embeds%20with%20clients%20to%20provide%20support%20for%20the%20products%20FDSEs%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Lin%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20enterprise%20startup%20Explo%2C%20worked%20as%20an%20FDSE%20at%20Palantir%20from%202017%20to%202019.%20He%20described%20the%20job%20as%20one%20where%20you%20needed%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20fast%20and%20break%20things%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20succeed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20wasn't%20always%20important%20to%20have%20a%20perfect%2C%20polished%20solution%20in%20order%20to%20succeed.%20You%20just%20needed%20to%20give%20your%20client%20something%20that%20worked%20well%2C%20quickly%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20was%2C%20'What%20does%20it%20take%20to%20win%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20client%3F'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20building%20faster%20to%20meet%20timelines%2C%20and%20that%20made%20our%20priorities%20slightly%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f49b0d7-d635-4c67-a9f6-07c80ed135ee%5C%22%3EFrom%20Forward%20Deployed%20to%20founder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Palantir%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story%2C%20so%20it's%20unclear%20exactly%20how%20many%20FDSEs%20the%20company%20has%20hired%20since%20the%20firm%20was%20founded%20in%202003%20or%20how%20many%20currently%20work%20there.%20There%20are%20around%20700%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20that%20list%20themselves%20as%20founders%20and%20say%20that%20Palantir%20was%20their%20former%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Lin%2C%20being%20embedded%20with%20clients%20gave%20engineers%20a%20chance%20to%20practice%20translating%20vague%20customer%20feedback%20into%20workable%20software%2C%20which%20is%20a%20skill%20that's%20proven%20essential%20in%20his%20current%20role%20leading%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForward%20Deployed%20Engineers%20will%20actually%20build%20software%20themselves%20and%20parse%20signal%20to%20noise%20what%20a%20customer%20is%20saying%20and%20figure%20out%20what's%20doable%20and%20reasonable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20exposure%20they%20get%20to%20the%20business%20side%20teaches%20you%20the%20tradeoffs%20between%20business%20development%20and%20product%20development%2C%20and%20as%20a%20founder%20you%20lean%20when%20it's%20okay%20to%20cut%20corners%20from%20an%20engineering%20perspective%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEliot%20Hodges%2C%20CEO%20at%20fintech%20startup%20Anduin%2C%20was%20an%20FDSE%20from%202012-2014.%20He%20remembers%20a%20relentless%20focus%20on%20outcome%20and%20impact%20for%20the%20client%2C%20and%20those%20values%20have%20stuck%20with%20him%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20now%20that%20he's%20running%20a%20startup%20of%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20was%20to%20bring%20in%20really%20ambitious%2C%20smart%20grads%20out%20of%20college%20and%20set%20them%20loose%20to%20be%20entrepreneurial%2C%20technical%20people%20to%20go%20out%20and%20pursue%20their%20own%20hypotheses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20unlike%20a%20traditional%20role%20at%20a%20consulting%20firm%2C%20forwa