E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competitors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompetition%3C%2Fa%3E%20heats%20up%20in%20the%20AI%20chip%20race%20for%20graphic%20processing%20units%20and%20application-specific%20integrated%20circuits%2C%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company%20isn't%20bothered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world's%20largest%20contract%20chipmaker%2C%20it%20makes%20them%20all%2C%20said%20CEO%20CC%20Wei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20left%20and%20right%2C%20and%20no%20matter%20how%20I%20look%20at%20it%2C%20the%20orders%20are%20all%20from%20TSMC%2C%26quot%3B%20Wei%20told%20local%20media%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20shareholder%20meeting%20in%20the%20northern%20Taiwanese%20city%20of%20Hsinchu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20TSMC%20reported%20a%2042%25%20rise%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20revenue%20from%20a%20year%20ago.%20It%20was%20the%20chip%20giant's%20fastest%20pace%20of%20growth%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20competitors%2C%20it's%20the%20indirect%20impact%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20tariffs%20that%20concerns%20TSMC's%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20have%20some%20impact%20on%20TSMC%2C%20but%20not%20directly.%20That's%20because%20tariffs%20are%20imposed%20on%20importers%2C%20not%20exporters%2C%26quot%3B%20Wei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tariffs%20can%20lead%20to%20slightly%20higher%20inflation%2C%20which%20may%20damp%20end%20demand%20and%20impact%20TSMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20anything.%20I%20am%20only%20afraid%20of%20the%20global%20economy%20slowing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20demand%20for%20AI%20chips%20has%20been%20robust%20and%20outpacing%20supply%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20March%2C%20TSMC%20announced%20an%20additional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw