rs%20are%20unfounded%2C%20but%20he%20does%20advise%20caution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFinkelman%20offers%20foreign%20workers%20and%20their%20employers%20tips%20on%20navigating%20the%20current%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20in%20mid-May%20with%2044-year-old%20Jason%20Finkelman%2C%20a%20business%20immigration%20lawyer%20in%20Austin.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20half%20lawyer%2C%20half%20therapist%20for%20my%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20help%20foreign%20nationals%20with%20employment%20and%20family%20immigration.%20On%20the%20employment%20side%2C%20I'm%20working%20with%20clients%20across%20a%20range%20of%20industries%2C%C2%A0including%20tech%2C%20semiconductor%2C%20energy%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%C2%A0research%2C%20and%20video%20gaming.%20Many%20of%20these%20are%20international%20entrepreneurs%20or%20investors%20looking%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20to%20start%20a%20business%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20unfounded%20fear%20among%20so%20many%20people%20right%20now%20about%20being%20deported.%20I'm%20having%20calls%20with%20foreign%20workers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20highly%20advanced%20degrees%20and%20are%20being%20sponsored%20by%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20and%20top%20startups%2C%20including%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20concerned%20about%20being%20deported%20for%20simply%20traveling%20abroad%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20even%20having%20calls%20with%20naturalized%20US%20citizens%20and%20people%20with%20green%20cards%20who%20have%20lived%20their%20lives%20for%20decades%20in%20this%20country%20without%20ever%20having%20committed%20a%20crime%2C%20or%20even%20received%20a%20parking%20ticket%2C%20but%20are%20seriously%20anxious%20about%20making%20routine%20international%20travel%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20keep%20reminding%20people%20that%20unless%20you%20have%20committed%20a%20major%20crime%2C%20it%20is%20extremely%20unlikely%20you'll%20be%20detained%20or%20removed%20from%20the%20US%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20status%20you%20are%20in%2C%20and%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20are%20hearing%20and%20seeing%20in%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20clients%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%20But%20it's%20not%20one%20or%20two%20people%20calling.%20It's%20dozens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc473b35-c9cc-499c-9b7c-ab5d34fe4252%5C%22%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20bringing%20stricter%20scrutiny%20to%20visa%20applications%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20picking%20up%20where%20it%20left%20off%2C%20making%20sure%20to%20be%20as%20strict%20as%20possible%20in%20adjudicating%20legal%20immigration%20to%20protect%20American%20jobs.%20It%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-h-1b-visa-applications-rejected-under-trump-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estricter%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20work%20visa%20applications%20and%20even%20routine%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20president%2C%20we%20would%20get%20a%20Request%20for%20Evidence%20when%20there%20was%20something%20that%20was%20objectively%20missing%20from%20the%20visa%20application.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-immigration-policy-donald-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20scrutinizing%20the%20subjective%20parts%20of%20an%20application%20to%20an%20extremely%20high%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-startups-that-sponsor-h-1b-visas-immigrant-workers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visas%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20classic%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20United%20States%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20officer%20will%20question%20whether%20the%20job%20being%20offered%20to%20the%20foreign%20national%20really%20requires%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20or%20whether%20the%20candidate's%20education%20really%20prepared%20them%20for%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20gotten%20notices%20essentially%20saying%20a%20cybersecurity%20analyst%20role%20might%20not%20require%20a%20degree%2C%20or%20questioning%20whether%20a%20software%20engineer%20really%20needs%20a%20bachelor's.%20We%20respond%20with%20letters%20from%20industry%20experts%20and%20even%20information%20from%20government%20websites%20to%20show%20that%20these%20jobs%20indeed%20require%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20increased%20scrutiny%2C%20I%20also%20want%20to%20include%20in%20the%20visa%20petition%20proof%20that%20the%20applicant's%20sponsoring%20company%20really%20exists%3A%20an%20office%20floor%20plan%20and%20photographs%20of%20the%20signage%20and%20the%20people%20at%20their%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20clients%20look%20at%20me%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20kidding.%26quot%3B%20I'm%20not%2C%20and%20I'm%20sorry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20kind%20of%20ridiculous%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20you%2030%20seconds%20to%20snap%20some%20pictures%20around%20the%20office%20and%20send%20them%20to%20me%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20getting%20a%20Request%20for%20Evidence%20when%20the%20USCIS%20officer%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20real%20company.%20Where%20is%20this%20person%20really%20going%20to%20work%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20play%20this%20game.%20I%20believe%20it's%20designed%20to%20frustrate%20US%20employers%20into%20giving%20up.%20Employers%20need%20the%20most%20skilled%20worker%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20that%20person%20is.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20a%20foreign%20worker.%20But%20there's%20so%20much%20effort%20and%20so%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fstuartanderson%2F2025%2F04%2F21%2Fimmigration-service-targets-h-1b-visa-holders-for-adverse-information%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoops%20to%20jump%20through%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20employers%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BForget%20it%2C%20let's%20just%20hire%20an%20American%20worker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfe4c8d0-dc0b-4b6b-b3da-f72c0801bb5f%5C%22%3EI'm%20advising%20visa%20holders%20to%20be%20overly%20cautious%20when%20traveling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20I%20advise%20my%20clients%20lately%20in%20preparation%20for%20international%20travel%2C%20including%20work-related%20trips%2C%20is%20very%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20ago%2C%20if%20a%20client%20had%20a%20valid%20work%20visa%20%E2%80%94%20say%20an%20H-1B%2C%20L-1%2C%20or%20O-1%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20you%20get%20some%20verbal%20questions%20from%20the%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20officer%2C%20but%20OK.%20You%20can%20prove%20that%20you%20work.%20You're%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20started%20seeing%20border%20officers%20apply%20extreme%20scrutiny%20to%20foreign%20nationals%20reentering%20the%20country%20with%20work%20visas.%20They'll%20ask%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20actually%20a%20job%20waiting%20for%20you%3F%20Is%20this%20a%20real%20company%3F%20Are%20you%20sure%20you're%20going%20to%20go%20back%20home%20after%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20environment%20where%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20officers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfchronicle.com%2Fbusiness%2Farticle%2FThey-don-t-like-Canadians-New-border-13761567.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20being%20stricter%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20foreign%20nationals%20traveling%20in%2C%20I'm%20advising%20all%20my%20clients%20to%20carry%20significant%20documentation%20with%20them%20to%20prove%20that%20they're%20currently%20employed%20and%20that%20they%20have%20this%20nonimmigrant%20intent%20to%20return%20to%20their%20home%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20should%20carry%20with%20them%20not