How%20to%20make%20sure%20you've%20got%20teams%20that%20have%20psychological%20safety%20to%20test%2C%20and%20try%2C%20and%20fail%20in%20the%20service%20of%20building%20new%20things.%20How%20you're%20being%20mindful%20of%20where%20people's%20skillset%20and%20energy%20are%20best%20used%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20project%20as%20it%20gets%20built.%20It's%20a%20whole%20different%20way%20to%20manage%20than%20the%20old%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22506f901e-5f41-4df3-a985-3584ffcf0a85%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20said%20you%20think%20every%20job%20will%20be%20different%20in%20a%20decade.%20What%20forces%20do%20you%20think%20will%20drive%20this%20change%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20we've%20seen%20change%20come%20in%20waves%3A%20remote%20work%2C%20shifting%20generational%20values%2C%20and%20rising%20worker%20expectations.%20But%20AI%20is%20different.%20It's%20a%20force%2C%20alongside%20breakthroughs%20in%20robotics%20and%20quantum%20computing%2C%20that's%20reshaping%20every%20job%2C%20in%20every%20sector%2C%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20AI%20will%20be%20the%20single%20biggest%20driver%20of%20work%20transformation%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20profound%20shifts%20the%20labor%20market%20has%20ever%20seen.%20We%20have%20a%20window%20right%20now%20to%20shape%20that%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20work%20more%20human%2C%20not%20less%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20we%20act%20with%20urgency%20and%20intention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b2ebc6e-a480-4b8e-b272-7cac5c6416ca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20the%20changing%20economy%20do%20you%20think%20will%20make%20managing%20people%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20tasks%2C%20particularly%20important%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20I%20think%20the%20role%20of%20manager%20is%20going%20to%20change%20is%20the%20same%20reason%20I%20think%20we're%20entering%20a%20new%20economy%2C%20which%20is%20that%20the%20role%20of%20humans%20at%20work%20is%20going%20to%20be%20more%20about%20coming%20up%20with%20new%20ideas%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20new%20inventions%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20new%20ways%20of%20work%20as%20an%20employee%20or%20new%20businesses%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%20That's%20going%20to%20be%20what%20will%20make%20work%20linger%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20world%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20manager%20at%20a%20company%2C%20you're%20trying%20to%20create%20the%20best%20environment%20for%20people%20to%20imagine%20and%20invent%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20different%20set%20of%20tasks%20than%20in%20the%20previous%20economy%20of%20just%20tracking%20people's%20tasks%20and%20making%20sure%20those%20tasks%20were%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241e9a8e0-c511-481b-8af2-0e3b233c55e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Great%20Recession%20and%20the%20pandemic%20both%20disrupted%20the%20careers%20of%20millennials%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20transitioned%20into%20management%20roles%20in%20recent%20years.%20Is%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20flattening%26quot%3B%20one%20more%20setback%20for%20the%20millennial%20career%20path%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20every%20single%20person%20is%20having%20their%20career%20clock%20reset%20right%20now.%20Everyone's%20job%20is%20changing%20on%20them%2C%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20changing%20jobs%2C%20and%20everyone's%20career%20trajectory%20is%20changing%20on%20them%2C%20even%20if%20they%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20change%20their%20career%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20something%20that%20people%20can%20approach%20with%20anxiety%20and%20fear%2C%20because%20we're%20biologically%20wired%20to%20be%20anxious%20and%20fearful%20of%20change%2C%20or%20it%20can%20be%20something%20that%20people%20see%20opportunity%20in%20so%20that%20they%20can%20start%20driving%20their%20career%20and%20their%20job%20in%20ways%20that%20give%20them%20more%20agency%20and%20more%20unique%20contribution%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E