5824.828-1748960928-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T195824.828-1748960928-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T195824.828-1748960928-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWearing%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20saree%20made%20Uma%20feel%20like%20a%20part%20of%20her%20was%20attending%20Uma%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20small%20detail%20was%20thought%20through%3A%20the%20waste%20segregation%20plan%20was%20communicated%20in%20advance%20to%20the%20catering%20team%2C%20ensuring%20wet%20and%20dry%20waste%20were%20properly%20managed.%20Her%20parents%20stood%20by%20her%20choices%2C%20proud%20and%20supportive%20of%20her%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20waste%20management%20services%20by%20Connect%20to%20Bhoomi%20were%20initially%20quoted%20at%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%20but%20Uma%2C%20working%20within%20a%20tight%20budget%2C%20found%20a%20way%20to%20negotiate%20a%20midpoint.%20A%20four-to-five-member%20team%20handled%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F203704%2Fgujarat-couple-zero-waste-wedding-donate-food-sustainable-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomposting%20and%20recycling%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20quietly%20educating%20guests%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20one%20tonne%20of%20waste%20was%20collected%20and%20responsibly%20managed%20%E2%80%94%20waste%20that%2C%20on%20any%20other%20day%2C%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20in%20landfills.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20an%20option%2C%20I%20would%20have%20saved%20even%20more%20and%20generated%20even%20less%20waste.%20But%20with%20what%20I%20had%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%20my%20bit%20for%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20story%20is%20proof%20that%20sustainable%20weddings%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20powerful.%20Even%20within%20the%20most%20traditional%20settings%2C%20meaningful%20change%20can%20begin%20with%20a%20single%20choice%2C%20a%20single%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20wedding%20industry%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20so%20does%20its%20footprint.%20But%20with%20small%20shifts%20%E2%80%94%20composting%20floral%20waste%2C%20rethinking%20decor%2C%20planning%20food%20redistribution%2C%20or%20opting%20for%20biodegradable%20invites%20%E2%80%94%20couples%20can%20begin%20to%20rewrite%20that%20story.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20like%20Uma%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F195354%2Fbengaluru-couple-eco-friendly-wedding-planning-tips-steel-cutlery-rent-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20behind%20more%20than%20just%20memories%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20leave%20behind%20something%20far%20more%20lasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Uma%20Ram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749009733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T200405.906_11zon-1748961285.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D443759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20if%20weddings%20didn%E2%80%99t%20leave%20behind%20heaps%20of%20trash%3F%20Meet%20Uma%20Ram%20from%20Chennai%2C%20who%20turned%20her%20big%20day%20into%20a%20celebration%20of%20love%20%E2%80%94%20for%20each%20other%20and%20for%20the%20planet.%20From%20composting%20one%20tonne%20of%20waste%20to%20wearing%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%2050-year-old%20saree%2C%20she%20proves%20that%20sustainability%20can%20be%20woven%20into%20every%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preet