20everything%20below.%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20his%20phone%20pings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20message%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20with%20a%20map%20of%20his%20farm.%20The%20message%20tells%20him%20where%20his%20crops%20are%20stressed%2C%20where%20pests%20might%20be%20hiding%2C%20and%20what%20he%20should%20do%20next%E2%80%94all%20in%20simple%20words%2C%20in%20his%20own%20language.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20guess%20anymore.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20waste%20money%20on%20extra%20sprays%20or%20wait%20for%20a%20local%20dealer%20to%20visit.%20A%20few%20taps%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20and%20the%20exact%20treatment%20he%20needs%20will%20arrive%20at%20his%20doorstep.%20For%20farmers%20like%20him%2C%20this%20tiny%20flying%20machine%20is%20not%20just%20about%20technology%20but%20peace%20of%20mind.%20And%20it%20all%20started%20because%20two%20young%20engineers%20brought%20their%20drones%20to%20the%20fields%2C%20simply%20hoping%20to%20help.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20where%20farming%20is%20as%20much%20a%20heritage%20as%20a%20livelihood%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417139%2Fhow-jasmine-transformed-tribal-lives-in-shahpur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerations%20of%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20relied%20on%20intuition%2C%20inherited%20wisdom%2C%20and%20the%20occasional%20advice%20of%20a%20pesticide%20dealer%20to%20tend%20their%20fields.%20But%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20climate-challenged%20world%2C%20where%20pests%20evolve%20faster%20than%20the%20solutions%20meant%20to%20stop%20them%2C%20such%20instinctive%20methods%20are%20no%20longer%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C