0India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20assumed%20we%20knew%20the%20answers%20because%20we%20were%20engineering%20students.%20Even%20though%20we%20did%20not%20know%20the%20answers%20back%20in%202015%2C%20we%20were%20curious%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20began%20their%20journey%20by%20visiting%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVKs)%20to%20better%20understand%20agricultural%20issues.%20While%20these%20centres%20offered%20scientific%20support%2C%20they%20were%20overstretched%2C%20typically%20serving%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20farmers%20across%20large%20regions.%20They%20realised%20that%20most%20growers%20still%20depended%20on%20advice%20from%20fellow%20farmers%20or%20local%20agrochemical%20dealers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20the%20real%20gap%20was%20not%20information%2C%20it%20was%20access%20to%20scientific%20data%20about%20the%20crop%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20began%20thinking%2C%20what%20if%20we%20could%20use%20the%20tools%20we%20already%20understood%2C%20like%20drones%20and%20imaging%2C%20to%20make%20that%20advice%20available%20to%20every%20farmer%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemote%20sensing%20and%20aerial%20imagery%20have%20already%20found%20wide%20application%20in%20defence%2C%20mining%2C%20and%20space%20exploration.%20The%20duo%E2%80%99s%20training%20had%20exposed%20them%20to%20technologies%20like%20hyperspectral%20imaging%2C%20which%20was%20famously%20used%20by%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20to%20detect%20minerals%20on%20the%20moon.%20Could%20the%20same%20tech%20be%20used%20to%20detect%20early%20signs%20of%20crop%20stress%20here%20on%20Earth%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3